title: 'jbb: The exemptions (I''m using the term broadly) cover most of what Colombia is know for. They must enormously reduce both (1) government revenue and (2) the incentive to try something new.'
pid: f5b63972-1d46-4f6a-8c7a-8145fc152354
body: |2-
  Why tie the country to masts like agriculture, mining and tourism?
